          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我闷坐花园，甚是无聊，到哪里去玩耍玩耍？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们到花园门外，玩玩去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此，带路！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏离座，随丫鬟同出门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呦，小姐，大事不好啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事惊慌？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面着火啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏看薛平贵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏想。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟，你远看？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是火！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "近观呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是一个花郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去将那花郎唤醒，带进花园，我有话讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏进门，归座。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花郎醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是丫鬟姐。唤我何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家小姐叫你进去，有话问你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有劳了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵站。丫鬟引薛平贵同进门。薛平贵向王宝钏作揖。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏自想。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住！看这花郎，两耳垂肩，双手过膝，乃大贵之相，为何落在乞讨之中？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯！我自有道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏对薛平贵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊花郎，你家住哪里，姓甚名谁？一一讲来，也好周济于你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐容禀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小姐在上容我禀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "细听花郎说分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "父母早已命归阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "薛平贵就是我的名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "家住本国长安地"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若问花郎名和姓"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家住本国长安地"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若问花郎名和姓"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听他言来自思忖："
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "容貌不像受苦的人——"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "龙眉虎目帝王尊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "莫非应在此人的身？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "彩球之事——"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "家住本国长安地"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "若问花郎名和姓"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "对他论，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏左右两顾。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又恐丫鬟在旁听。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊丫鬟，去到绣房取银子一锭、衣服一件。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊花郎，方才你言道家中父母双亡，你可有……"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有妻室呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏用袖掩面作羞。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐说哪里话来！落在乞讨之中，哪里来得银钱娶妻呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有一言，不好启齿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐有何金言，尽管请讲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊花郎，我对你实说了吧：我父约定二月二日，在十字街前，高搭彩楼，抛球"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "招赘。是日你可站在楼前。倘若姻缘有分，也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "里面都是王孙公子，哪有花郎之份？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我有一言，你且听了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二月二日事有准，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "切莫错过好光阴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你是天台路上的人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐，银两、衣裳在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "付与花郎，叫他去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "辞别小姐出园门，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵作揖，欲出门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "转来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小姐还有何话云？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你若不来失了信，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "就是忘恩负义的人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "小姐不必细叮咛，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "平贵岂是负义的人？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵出门，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奴家暗把天祝定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王宝钏",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二月二日配良姻。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王宝钏、丫鬟同下。）"
        }
      ],
